posting_body: ['To schedule a tour', 'We now book our tour appointments online!', 'Please call or text us at', 'show contact info', 'to self-schedule from your phone!', 'Book your appointment online today or anytime 24/7!', 'Property Description', 'The Harbor Point Apartments is a waterfront community located on Richardson Bay.', 'Nestled on the picturesque Strawberry Point in Mill Valley, we offer luxury resort living, a state-of-the-art fitness center and a premier tennis club, all with spectacular views of San Francisco, Tiburon and the Bay.', 'Just off the 101 freeway and minutes from San Francisco, Harbor Point is the ideal location for commuters and those who like a retreat from the City.', 'It’s also the ultimate destination for great outdoor aficionados: walk, bike, swim, play tennis, kayak, or simply relax, wine and dine at Harbor Point’s restaurant directly over the water.', 'Details', 'Availability date:', 'August 5, 2022', 'Pets:', 'Cats, Small Dogs (< 25lb), Large Dogs (> 25lb)', 'Pet notes:', 'Security deposit increases by $500 per pet.', 'Breed restrictions apply.', 'Deposit:', '500, 600, 700, 800', 'Leasing options:', '12 months', 'Leasing notes:', 'We do offer the option of a 6- month lease at a $500.00 upcharge per month.', 'Application fee:', '$53.33', 'Amenities', 'Included in Utilities Cost:', 'Utilities Cost:', 'Based on Usage', 'Laundry:', 'In Unit, Shared', 'Parking type:', 'Garage, Covered', 'Parking notes:', 'Appliances:', 'Dishwasher, Refrigerator, Garbage disposal, Microwave, Range/Oven', 'Exterior:', 'Balcony/patio, Deck, Garden', 'Heating/cooling:', 'Wiring:', 'Cable-ready', 'Facilities and Recreation:', 'Shared pool, Fitness center, Clubhouse, Barbecue, Tennis court, Restaurant', 'Security and Access:', 'Elevator', 'Views:', 'City, Water', 'Additional features:', 'Tile floor, Granite countertop, Fireplace, Vaulted ceiling, Sauna, Hot tub / Spa, Non-Smoking Property', 'Offered by:', 'Harbor Point', 'Equal Housing Opportunity']
